#North America: 20M km2
deserts
- Sonoran (Baja California)
- Mojave (Death Valley)
- Great Basin (Great Salt Lake)
- Chihuahuan
mountains
- Cordillera (Cascades + Rocky Mountains + Sierra Nevada + Sierra Madre)
- Appalachians
waters
- Mississippi + Missouri + Ohio + Arkansas
- Rio Grande
- Colorado (Grand Canyon + Antelope Canyon + Rainbow Bridge)
- Columbia + Snake
- Yukon
- Mackenzie (Great Bear Lake + Great Slave Lake)
- St. Lawrence + Great Lakes (Superior, Michigan, Huron, Erie, Niagara Falls, Ontario)
- Red (Lake Winnipeg)
peninsulas
- Yucatán
- Florida
- Nova Scotia
- Labrador
- Alaska
others
- Monument Valley (butte)
- El Capitan + Yosemite Falls
- Mexican Plateau

#South America: 18M km2, most wet
Isthmus of Panama + Darién Gap
deserts
- Atacama
mountains
- Andes (Lake Titicaca)
- Guiana Highlands (tepui)
waters
- Amazon + Madeira + Negro (Amazon rainforest)
- Paraná (Iguazu Falls)
- Orinoco (Angel Falls)
- Kaieteur Falls
- Lake Maracaibo

#Africa: 30M km2
deserts
- Sahara
- Kalahari + Namib
- Karoo
- Ogaden
mountains
- Atlas
- Ethiopian Highlands
- Mount Kilimanjaro
- Table Mountain
- Great Escarpment (Drakensberg)
waters
- Nile (white + blue) + Lake Victoria
- Lake Chad
- Zambezi (Victoria Falls)
- Limpopo
- Orange
- Okavango (to Kalahari)
- Cunene (Ruacana Falls)
- Cuanza (Calandula Falls)
- Congo
- Niger
- Volta
- Senegal
peninsulas
- Horn of Africa
others
- Ngorongoro Crater

#Asia: 44M km2
India
- Deccan Plateau + Ghats
- mountains: Himalayas + Karakoram
- deserts: Thar
- rivers: Indus + Ganges + Brahmaputra
Middle east
- deserts: Arabian + Syrian
- mountains: Taurus + Zagros + Alborz + Caucasus
- terrain: Anatolian Plateau + Armenian Highlands + Iranian Plateau
- rivers: Euphrates + Tigris
- lakes: Van + Urmia + Sevan
- peninsulas: Anatolia (Asia Minor), Arabia, Sinai
Central
- deserts: Karakum + Kyzylkum
- mountains: Hindukush + Pamir + Tian Shan + Altai
- rivers: Amu Darya + Syr Darya + Helmand
- lakes: Caspian Sea + Aral Sea + Balkhash + Issyk Kul
East
- deserts: Gobi + Taklamakan (Tarim Basin)
- mountains: Kunlun + Tibetan Plateau
- rivers: Yangtze + Huang He + Pearl River, Amur, Mekong + Irrawaddy
- peninsulas: Malay (Kra Isthmus), Korea
North
- rivers: Ob, Yenisey, Lena
- lakes: Baikal
- peninsulas: Kamchatka

#Europe: 10M km2
North
- mountains: Scandinavian
- lakes: Vänern + Vättern, Onega + Ladoga, Saimaa, Peipus
- peninsulas: Scandinavian + Jutland + Kola
West
- mountains: Alps + Jura + Black Forest, Pyrenees + Cantabrian, Apennines, Central Massif, Eifel + Ardennes
- rivers: Elbe/Labe + Oder/Odra, Weser + Rhine, Seine + Loire + Garonne, Rhone, Po, Tagus/Tejo, Thames, Duero, Guadalquivir
- lakes: Geneva + Constance/Bodensee + Garda
- peninsulas: Iberia, Italia + Calabria, Istria, Brittany
East
- mountains: Carpathians, Dinaric Alps, Ural
- rivers: Danube, Vistula, Dnieper + Don + Volga
- lakes: Balaton + Neusiedl
- peninsulas: Peloponnese, Crimea

#Australia: 8M km2, most arid
deserts: Great Victoria + Great Sandy + Tanami + Simpson + Gibson
mountains: Great Dividing Range, Uluru / Ayers Rock
rivers: Murray + Darling
lakes: Eyre + Torrens
peninsulas: Cape York
